    <script type="text/javascript" src="&#x2F;dist&#x2F;client&#x2F;header.f1cf69e28d42d8c77c08.js"></script><div id="root"><main class="FilmPage__Landmark-sc-2prf8w-0 kiRyNW"><header class="HeroBasic__Hero-sc-1as804s-0 kvSaef"><div class="Hero__text"><h1>Wanda (1970)</h1><div class="Hero__standfirst">Barbara Loden’s tough, unsentimental portrait of a woman adrift in the industrial heartlands of the north-eastern United States.</div></div><div class="Hero__children"><div class="FilmPage__ActionButtonWrapper-sc-2prf8w-3 eMNMIC"><a href="http://shop.bfi.org.uk/dvd-blu-ray/women-make-film-collection/wanda-blu-ray.html" class="Button__PrimaryButton-sc-8dp7u4-0 iGKFPz light">Buy on <!-- -->Blu-Ray<!-- --> <span class="FilmPage__ButtonPrice-sc-2prf8w-2 eeHuLI">£<!-- -->28.99</span></a></div></div></header><div><div class="FilmPage__BreadcrumbContainer-sc-2prf8w-16 jXpcaj"><nav role="navigation" aria-label="breadcrumbs" class="Breadcrumbs__Nav-sc-xbclhh-0 exdrCH"><ol class="Breadcrumbs__Outer-sc-xbclhh-1 creMhq"><li class="Breadcrumbs__Crumb-sc-xbclhh-3 tJVyx"><a href="/" data-tracking="breadcrumb" class="Breadcrumbs__BreadcrumbLink-sc-xbclhh-4 kpflcc">Watch and discover</a></li><li class="Breadcrumbs__Crumb-sc-xbclhh-3 tJVyx"><a href="/sight-and-sound" data-tracking="breadcrumb" class="Breadcrumbs__BreadcrumbLink-sc-xbclhh-4 kpflcc">Sight and Sound</a></li><li class="Breadcrumbs__Crumb-sc-xbclhh-3 tJVyx"><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time" data-tracking="breadcrumb" class="Breadcrumbs__BreadcrumbLink-sc-xbclhh-4 kpflcc">The Greatest Films of All Time</a></li><li class="Breadcrumbs__Crumb-sc-xbclhh-3 tJVyx">Wanda</li></ol><ol class="Breadcrumbs__MobileOuter-sc-xbclhh-2 hHFrmv"><li class="Breadcrumbs__Crumb-sc-xbclhh-3 tJVyx"><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time" data-tracking="breadcrumb" class="Breadcrumbs__BreadcrumbLink-sc-xbclhh-4 kpflcc">&lt;  <!-- -->The Greatest Films of All Time</a></li></ol></nav></div></div><div class="TextContent-sc-jn8we1-0 FilmPage__FilmTextContent-sc-2prf8w-5 dhFXfd lbJxYz"><article class="PageContainer__MainContentWrapper-sc-jezgjv-1 deevsk child_page"><div class="Text__Outer-sc-1acyvkb-0 iESPyA text_block"><p>“How can a woman ever afford to be both wayward and astray? Wanda showed us how it’s done without telling us why (or why not). Loden’s crisp sensitivity and sudden spikes of ambivalence are immortalised in her debut, and only, feature film as a director.” <strong>Savina Petkova</strong></p>

<p>“Flies in the face of the generic American road movie’s petro-capitalist and patriarchal fantasies.” <strong>Becca Voelcker</strong></p>

<p>“Quite simply, there is nothing else like this film.” <strong>Anna Backman Rogers</strong></p>
